high_descs: Turn around and go to the right of the table behind you.
Take the mug from the coffee maker on the table.
Turn around and go to the sinks behind you.
Fill the mug with water in the left sink.
Turn around and return to the right side of the table behind you.
Place the mug at the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with water at the coffee maker.

high_descs: Pick up the mug from the coffee machine.
Bring the mug to the sink on the right.
Fill up the mug with water.
Bring the mug to the coffee machine.
Put the mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug filled with water on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the table with the coffee maker.
Pick up the cup on the coffee maker.
Turn around and head towards the sink.
Place the cup into the left sink, turn on the faucet, wash the cup, turn off the faucet, and pick up the cup.
Turn around and head towards the coffee maker on the table.
Place the cup back on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Wash the cup on the coffee maker.
